er Stone誹謗<br />\n告入左, 原本係索償1億美金<br />\n後尾叫Roger Stone登報道歉就算"},{"pid":"7a1cf24e7ab1db3e2559c7991f3ba1776a8d27b4","tid":1183802,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64c3b94c61a9cd785856856a1d45bcb74cf0f9c6","tid":1183802,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T08:21:32.000Z","msg":"郭sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓋sir <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:48:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5455ffa39815153162fee3b3c755bc5432cdaa","tid":1183802,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:55:29.000Z","msg":"條友未夠班幫樓挽鞋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a07c606f1bbaf3469b1cc2a41759afec157bdf7f","tid":1183802,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T09:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條友未夠班幫樓主挽鞋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1a871f3b8e8036236ef4d08dc57b198abd6c589e","tid":1183802,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T10:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5467ebba1af26a1c4a0fbe30b71e74592243e2","tid":1183802,"uid":75782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T12:36:09.000Z","msg":"唔通信班五毛狗咩 郭個反共網絡好大<br />\n仲有班農支持"}]}